---
import { SITE_LOCATION } from '../../consts';
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-page px-6 sm:px-8">
		<div class="pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
			<p
				class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-2xs tracking-[0.18em] text-fg-subtle uppercase"
			>
				<span class="relative flex h-1.5 w-1.5">
					<span
						class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-positive opacity-75"
					></span>
					<span class="relative inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-positive"></span>
				</span>
				Taking on new projects · {SITE_LOCATION}
			</p>

			<h1
				class="mt-10 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-balance sm:mt-12 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"
			>
				The internal tools your business runs on —
				<span class="text-fg-muted">built, shipped, and still running.</span>
			</h1>

			<p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty sm:text-xl">
				<span class="text-fg">Roga Digital</span> is a software studio that designs, ships, and maintains
				the tools businesses depend on — dashboards, integrations, AI features, and the internal apps
				your team uses every day.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
				<a
					href="/contact"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-fg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-bg transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
				>
					Book a call
					<svg
						width="14"
						height="14"
						viewBox="0 0 16 16"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="1.5"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"
						aria-hidden="true"
					>
						<path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"></path>
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a
					href="/work"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-border-strong px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-fg transition-colors hover:border-fg-subtle"
				>
					See selected work
				</a>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-10 max-w-2xl text-sm text-fg-muted text-pretty">
				In production now: a TELUS platform serving 2,500+ field technicians, and client systems
				running continuously since 2023.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
